text.text: The aquarium located under an HDB block is spacious and well-lit. It offers a wide range of fish and aquarium accessories. The floor is kept dry, which is different from some other aquariums.

text.text: A place full of healthy fishes, a vast variety water plants and different aquarium accessories. It is located under a HDB opposite the Geylang Bahru market behind the NTUC. The staffs here are all very polite and have good knowledge of the items and livestock they are selling. This aquarium is certainly a one-stop shop to go to, if you are thinking of starting a new hobby today. I was there to stock up on some supplies for my turtle tank, and they have everything I need as well. Glad I made this trip.
